<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM19">
<l>tamakkeṉṟu miṉpaṇi ceytirup pēmukkut tāmorunā</l>
<l>ḷemakkoṉṟu coṉṉā laruḷuṅko lāmiṇai yātumiṉṟic</l>
<l>cumakkiṉṟa piḷḷaiveḷḷēṟoppa toṉṟutoṇ ṭaikkaṉivā</l>
<l>yumaikkeṉṟu tēṭip peṟātuṭa ṉēkoṇṭa vuttamarē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To us who always keep doing pleasing service to him, if one day we speak</l>
<l>about one thing for us, will he grace [it], the Highest one who gave as soon as he had found</l>
<l>[and] obtained [it], thinking “for Umā with the mouth of a Toṇṭai fruit,</l>
<l>one equal to the infant white bull that bears him, without anything like that exists.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
